00:40:00.716 --> 00:40:01.477
Su Majestad,

00:40:02.397 --> 00:40:04.797
has hecho al príncipe heredero
arrodillarse fuera del palacio

00:40:05.076 --> 00:40:06.636
durante toda la tarde.

00:40:07.236 --> 00:40:08.277
